social_posts.post_text: Thinkin Bout You by @blonded  This ones for all the homies missin their shawties 🤧. Long overdue collaboration with the legendary @shaan.ramaprasad He also blessed “Ride Alone” (my latest single) with strings! If you haven’t heard it already the link is in the bio! Much love ♥️
We really knee deep into this music thing. There's no going back now. GODSPEEEDDDD 🌷 CITY LIGHTS X @thisizintense IS OUT NOWWW!!! @mooks.vzn 📽️
Coming to a parking garage somewhere near you. Remember to have fun with it 🐸. Big thanks to @simrancheemaszn for elevating the style!
Yup…and so the Punjabi finally came out hehe. Hope y’all enjoy this medley. Greatly appreciate the love and support ♥️ so much I can’t wait to share with everyone! Stay blessed ✌🏽
Trying something new, come vibe with me :) thank you so much for all the love. Exciting things coming up and I can’t wait for you to hear! Stay blessed y’all…deuces ✌🏽💐

Something Stupid by Frank Sinatra. Flopped a word in there but oh well. Life goes on. Welcome to all the new folks who have recently followed and showed a tremendous amount of love and support ♥️ My names Gurtêj and it’s senti hour every hour ;) Kick back relax and come vibe out with me 🌊
Pink Matter by Frank Ocean. It’s getting juicy folks 🙆‍♀️. Buckle in. Catch me performing at 4N Nights in Toronto June 17th!!! Thank you for all the love 🌷. EP announcement coming soon!

Sup y’all! This is me singing without a fancy mic and all. I’ve found that if you focus of being the best at your craft…everything kinda falls into place. Stay in a state of becoming. Give thanks for all the beautiful life there is around. Everything comes down to a choice and I think love is something you choose. It’s a little dance you do with the universe everyday. This caption is all over the place. Oh well. Thanks for sticking around. I know I’ve said I have so much music I can’t wait to share and your probably wondering like…bro when the next drop….it’s coming :)

Going by @hermusicofficial my posts keep glitching y’all apologize for the repost. had a lot of fun making this one. Love the cadence in this song. Can’t wait to share more about my next single!! My goal from the very beginning of this journey has been to create art that feels timeless and authentic to my vision. Something that can endure the rest of time. To me that’s what great art is. I feel like I’ve grown so much as an creator in these past few months. Thank you all so much for the love ♥️ ….all in due time…gonna go watch the Kanye doc now byeeeeeeee

@karanaujla_official - admiring you X don’t - @teddysphotos loving the new album. This was a really fun piece to work on. @ikky.music and the team behind the album absolutely killed the production. hope you enjoy this piece. Single announcement soon. Much love 🫶🏽

Paranoia Purple by @yebbasmith . Life’s been feeling slow but fast at the same time. The energy in the world seems to be getting stranger. When I was younger I thought I’d have it all figured out by now…news flash I don’t. Truth is you kinda always stay “figuring it out”. There is no end in this creative pursuit. Just got to make sure to stop and smell the flowers in the garden from time to time. We’ve come a long way and there’s still a long ways to go. I know I say this but believe me I have some very exciting things I can’t wait to share soon 🤞🏽 Thank you for all the love. Means the world. Stay becoming 🙏🏽 ♥️
Get you by @danielcaesar Sunday vibes. Hope yall enjoy this little clip 💛
Getting a little experimental. Phir le aya dil (Hindi) X Galerna (Spanish) thank you for all the love 💛

I find a lot of healing in music. I hope you find some solace here as well. Here’s a clip from last night I would’ve never posted beacuse it’s not “good enough”- but why hold on to it. I think the problem is that I think too much. Care too much. I analyze instead of feeling. There’s a tornado of thoughts and feelings a lot of the times up there. Trying to find moments of stillness. The older I get, the more questions and confused I feel like I become. The more I started to “care” of how I was perceived. The enemy is yourself posed as a question (truisms 4 dummies - headache) I have faith the journey. One day at a time. I can’t wait for yall to hear the original music I’ve been cooking up. The team and I have spent countless hours creating these pieces. Coming the new year I’ll announce their release. Thank you all for your love and continued support. Godspeed ✌🏽
